    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for parts or as a dedicated restoration project. The engine currently requires a major overhaul and the transmission is slipping, making it unreliable for daily transport. Externally, there is significant rust along the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with several large dents and faded paint. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional dashboard cluster. Sold strictly as-is.",
