    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently struggles to stay idle and there is a noticeable transmission slip, making it unsafe for long-distance driving in its current state. Externally, the body shows heavy rust along the rocker panels, several large dents, and fading clear coat throughout. The interior has multiple tears in the upholstery and the electronic console is non-functional. This car is best suited as a parts donor or a major restoration project for an experienced mechanic.",
